PLAN- 6-SKYLIGHTS,EIK, D/R AND L/R, ENCLOSED PORCH W/ WATER VIEWS, FULL 4 PIECE BATH, MSTR BDRM, 2ND BDRM USED AS AN OPEN OFFICE AREA ( easily converted back to a private bdrm) HW FLRS THRU OUT.
APARTMENT- RENOVATED 2016- 1 BDRM, NEW BATH, NEW KITCHEN
